  "title": "ISic001421. I.Sicily inscription 001421",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Καλικράτε̄ς καλὸς ὁ Κρασίπου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Καλικράτε̄ς\">Κ̣αλικράτε̄ς</span> καλὸς̣ [ὁ] <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κρασίπου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Κρασίπου\">Κ̣[ρα?]σίπου</span></span></span> καὶ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Λο̄σαις Ἀμουνφί\n                    ο̄νος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Λο̄σαις\">Λο̄σαις</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀμουνφί\n                    ο̄νος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀμουνφί\n                    ο̄νος\">Ἀμουνφί-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ο̄ν̣ος</span></span></span> τοκε͂ς ͱοί κ’ ἔλαβον χο̄́ρε̄[ν] ͱο͂ι ͱο̄ς μνε̄́μα μεῖν-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>αι καὶ ͱο̄ς </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Καλικράτε̄ς καλὸς ὁ Κρασίπου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Καλικράτε̄ς\">.ΑΛΙΚΡΑΤΕ̄Σ</span>ΚΑΛΟ.[.]<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κρασίπου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Κρασίπου\">.[..]ΣΙΠΟΥ</span></span></span>ΚΑΙ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Λο̄σαις Ἀμουνφί\n                    ο̄νος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Λο̄σαις\">ΛΟ̄ΣΑΙΣ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀμουνφί\n                    ο̄νος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀμουνφί\n                    ο̄νος\">ΑΜΟΥΝΦΙ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>Ο̄.ΟΣ</span></span></span>ΤΟΚΕΣͰΟΙΚΕΛΑΒΟΝΧΟ̄ΡΕ̄[.]ͰΟΙͰΟ̄ΣΜΝΕ̄ΜΑΜΕΙΝ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΑΙΚΑΙͰΟ̄Σ</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001421_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001421_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001421.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001421-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><p>  </p><p>After Manganaro 1996</p>  <p></p></div>  <p class=\"note\">(Jeffery Archive: Καλικράτε̄ς καλὸ. ͱο το [καλ]ίπου νοθος Ἀισα Μουνφί)</p>  <p class=\"note\">(Jeffery Archive: με[λ]εν αμεινο)</p>  <p class=\"note\">(Jeffery Archive: -ν καὶ ͱο̄ς αμ’ει{ν}αι)</p>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 46.1260.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> 43.0633 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> 1997.0723 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282</a></li><li> 1967.0709 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282</a></li><li> Jeffery J.WC.Kamar.15b.p.01(2)-02(2) <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002295\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002295</a></li><li> Manganaro 1965 193-194 tav.68.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841</a></li><li> Dubois 1989 <a href=\"http://www.persee.fr/doc/efr_0000-0000_1989_cat_119_1\" target=\"_blank\">104</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187</a></li><li> Jeffery, Johnston 1990 459 no.15b <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000677\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000677</a></li><li> Curbera 1993 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001490\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001490</a></li><li> Manganaro 1996 60-63 no.13 fig. 24-26 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001817\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001817</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
